anting on about how the elves are our friends and how the Shanks are ruining relations with the other &quot;light&quot; races.  Again I had to point out to them that this is us (human strains) vs. everyone else.  Even heard someone /say that they were going to petition the Shanks...didn't catch the name though.  Yeah, I know I am ranting but I am mad...came to a red server to get away from people like this but I guess whiners and complainers are everywhere.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#a8a8a8><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ukattriaminx.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kattria Minx </A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Council of Elders</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>11/11/00</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>10:10:29 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: The Rules of the Server...Why Are They Ignored?</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Yes, I find it very funny when someone says they are going to petition us for trying to kill them. :) <br>
