Historically speaking, I believe the shift from the originally intended 4-team environment, towards good versus evil (GvE), came about because the evil team dominated the lands -- Freeport in particular. In addition, I'm sure that it feels more significant in many players minds, to be &quot;evil&quot; or &quot;good&quot; rather than being &quot;human,&quot; &quot;shortie&quot; or &quot;elf&quot; -- so a GvE may be more relevant to the human psyche. <br>
<br>
